3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper proposes a new approach for automatic defect recognition using deep learning techniques. 
4. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with recognizing specific patterns on steel sheets. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also less likely but possible as the paper deals with image recognition and processing.
